zookeeper extension changelog

Version 0.3.0
-------------
	* Ability to specify max tries per request with delay and backoff multiplier
	* Throw exceptions when unexpected conditions arise
	* Adjust Zookeeper API calls to LOG() to use newer syntax
	* Requires libzookeeper >= 3.5.0

Version 0.2.2
-------------
	* PHP 5.4 compatibility
	* Sample PHP class for using zookeeper
	* Fix NOTCONNECTED_STATE issue
	* Various other fixes

Version 0.2.1
-------------

Version 0.2.0
-------------

Version 0.1.0
-------------
	* Initial release
